ic and feature-packed WordPress theme designed for creating captivating travel and tour booking websites. This theme is your gateway to crafting diverse travel platforms, be it for city tours, trekking adventures, cycling expeditions, or thrilling jungle safaris.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Travel Explorer, combined with the WP Travel Engine plugin, adds lots of features to your site. This compatibility allows you to create a myriad of tour combinations, travel destinations, trip types, and activities. It\'s your all-in-one toolkit for launching a comprehensive website to market and sell your travel packages.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>What sets Travel Explorer apart is its strong focus on SEO and mobile optimization. This ensures that your website not only ranks better in search engine results but also provides a seamless browsing experience across all devices.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With Travel Explorer, you\'re not just building a travel website; you\'re creating an immersive digital experience that guides your customers through their travel journey, right from the moment they start dreaming about their trip to the point they book their adventure.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Travel Explorer is for you:<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want to <strong>build a modern and beautifully designed travel and tour booking site<\\/strong>.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want to fine-tune your website as per your preferences.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want to <strong>quickly build your website without writing a single line of code<\\/strong>.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want a mobile-friendly website to provide a better user experience to your customers.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want to <strong>generate more leads and boost your conversion<\\/strong> through trip bookings.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want a site that is easier to navigate for your customers.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want a <strong>speed-optimized and SEO-friendly site<\\/strong> to rank better on search engines.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>You want world-class support from experts to assist you with your website.<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading -->\\n<h2 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Features of Travel Explorer<\\/h2>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Ready to Import Starter Sites<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can select from a wide selection of travel-related templates to create your website. The templates include unique designs to develop an online travel booking site.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Speed Optimized for Great Performance<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Website loading speed is <strong>essential for a website\'s higher ranking and offering the best user experience<\\/strong> to your visitors. As a result, we\'ve worked hard to improve this theme to load fast.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Core Web Vital Optimized<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Look no further than Travel Explorer if you\'re looking for a website <strong>optimized for Core Web Vitals<\\/strong> and provides a higher score on Google PageSpeed Insights.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Loads Fast<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The default theme is designed to be lightweight, load fast and make fewer requests.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Install Pre-Design Demo with One Click<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With Travel Explorer, you can<strong> instantly access an array of pre-made templates<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Install Exact Demo<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Within a few minutes, you can have your site up and running with the template of your choice.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Customize Imported Demo<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can <strong>tailor the imported demo content to exactly match your preferences<\\/strong>. Simply use the page builder to edit the template and make whatever changes you desire.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Access to all the Latest Demos<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You will get access to all new free starter site templates as soon they are added to the collection.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Gorgeous Responsive\\/Mobile Friendly Design<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Because most users access the internet on their mobile devices, having a responsive\\/mobile-friendly website is essential. Furthermore, Google considers this to be one of the ranking criteria.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>It <strong>passes the Google Mobile-Friendly Test<\\/strong> to ensure that your visitors have a pleasant experience on all devices and screen sizes. It also aids in search engine rankings.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">SEO Optimised for Better Ranking<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Our SEO experts and developers worked together to <strong>implement the best SEO practices<\\/strong> possible for this theme.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">SEO Optimised<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>This theme is SEO-friendly, and we\'ve built it with an SEO-friendly structure.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Schema Friendly Markup<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>This theme uses schema markup to communicate with search engines, improving content understanding.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Last Updated On<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Search engines love fresh content, which is why it\'s essential for you to have regular updates. Search engines will take notice of the date on which your content was last updated.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Built-in Breadcrumb<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Adding a breadcrumb trail to your website makes navigation quicker for users and helps search engines index your pages more effectively.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Unlimited Colour Options<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Do you want to customize your website to reflect your company\'s style? Travel Explorer <strong>offers a variety of colour options for customization<\\/strong> throughout various components of your website.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Typography Options<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The choice of typefaces significantly impacts the site\'s appearance and overall feel. Therefore, the <strong>typography in this theme is highly customizable<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">1400+ Google Fonts<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With over 1400 unique Google Fonts, Travel Explorer is always up-to-date with the latest fonts!<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Customization Control<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You have precise control over the typefaces you want to use. Choose the font size, weight, transformation, and other preferred features.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Host Fonts Locally<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Hosting your fonts locally can <strong>make your site GDPR compliant and improve the loading speed<\\/strong>. This theme makes it hassle-free for you to host the desired font types locally.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Easy to use Theme Settings Panel with Live Preview<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Travel Muni neatly organizes the settings panel making it simpler to find your way around and configure the settings to your liking. Also, you have the opportunity to <strong>view changes in real time before making them public<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">WP Travel Engine Compatible<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With Travel Explorer, you can easily create a fully functional travel booking website using WP Travel Engine. This plugin is <strong>trusted by over 10,000 agencies<\\/strong> and makes adding tours and selling them easy.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Trips Search<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The Advanced Trips Search feature is one of the most remarkable features of this plugin. With it, visitors can <strong>quickly find trips based on duration, destination, price, activities, and other search criteria<\\/strong>, improving their browsing experience.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Destinations Page&nbsp;<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The plugin smartly arranges your tour destinations so visitors can easily find different tours based on the places they love to travel.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Activities Page<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Your travel booking site may offer various activities, including but not limited to hiking, bird watching, jungle safari and city tour. You can also create trip packages with multiple activities to make it easier for visitors to find and book the perfect vacation.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Trip Types Page<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>People searching for vacations also look for tours based on different factors, like if the tour is child-friendly, how much nature is involved, and the budget. You can simplify their search by creating trip types and categorizing your tours under them.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">PayPal Payment Gateway<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can use the <strong>PayPal Payment gateway built-in to WP Travel Engine<\\/strong> to collect payments for your tours. You will receive the amount in your Paypal account after your visitor purchases a tour.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":4} -->\\n<h4 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Coupons<\\/h4>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>By offering discounts to customers, you will increase the likelihood of them booking more trips, making your tours more successful. This plugin has a built-in feature for this purpose.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Elementor Compatible<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>With Travel Explorer, you can use Elementor- a powerful drag-and-drop builder that makes it easy to create or edit any design. <strong>Travel Explorer\'s templates can be quickly edited using this plugin<\\/strong>.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The best thing about this free plugin is that no coding is involved, and you can test the modifications in real time before publishing them. Furthermore, you have many design options and extensive customization capabilities to fine-tune your website.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Gutenberg Compatible<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The Travel Explorer theme is also compatible with the Gutenberg editor. As a result, you can rapidly create your site using blocks and arranging them as you choose.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Header Options<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The header can be used to include essential information. For example, you may include contact information, a header button, social media links, and even modify the mobile header.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Not only that, but you also have more options for customizing the appearance of your site header.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Blog Page Settings<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can find some essential settings to fine-tune your blog page. It includes sidebar layouts, and image and post settings.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Page Settings<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>On Travel Explorer, you can tailor your pages to look how you want. For example, you show or hide the page title, choose the default sidebar layout, enable or disable featured image and more.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Powerful Customization for Single Post<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Our new advanced blogging control offers you more flexibility to customize the appearance of your single posts. Some notable features include:<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list -->\\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>4 sidebar layouts<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Sortable Post Meta Order<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Settings to enable or disable Author box, Post tags and pagination<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Advanced Related Posts settings<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\\n<li>Advanced Comment Settings<\\/li>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list-item --><\\/ul>\\n<!-- \\/wp:list -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Advanced Archive Page Settings<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can also adjust the appearance of archive pages, such as category archive, author archive, and search archive.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Button Customization<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>In Travel Explorer, you can modify the button appearance using advanced controls such as padding, margin, typography, and colours.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Customizable 404 Page<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>This theme allows you to liven up your 404 page by adding your preferred image and displaying your blog posts.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Social Media Integration<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Including social media links in your header can help increase your online visibility. You can link to popular platforms such as Facebook, Twitter, TikTok, Instagram, Pinterest, Trip Advisors and more.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Scroll to Top<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The Scroll to Top feature is a handy tool that lets visitors quickly get back to the top of your site with just one click. This makes for a better user experience, saving them time and effort.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Sticky Widget<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The sticky widget is a useful feature that makes the previous widget sticky in the sidebar. You may include a Call-to-Action, email subscription, or anything else you wish to get your visitors\' attention.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">4 Footer Widget Areas<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can have a maximum of four footer widget areas in this theme. The width is automatically distributed based on the number of configured widget areas.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Footer Settings<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Travel Explorer provides more customization features, such as changing the footer background colours and images of different payment gateways.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Footer Copyright<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>You can customize the footer copyright text.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Cross Browser Compatible<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Our developers have tested Travel Explorer with all leading browsers, like Google Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Microsoft Edge and Brave. Consequently, your website will load similarly on these browsers to give the same experience to every one of your visitors.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Easy Legibility<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Fitted with the correct typeface, colour, spacing, and other design elements, this theme makes your content more readable. As a result, your visitors can browse your site without experiencing eyestrain.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">RTL Scripts Ready<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>If you write in an RTL (right-to-left) language such as Arabic or Hebrew, this theme will enable you to build your site quickly.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Translation Ready<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>The theme is completely ready to be translated, so you can easily create a website in any language.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Polylang and WPML Compatible (Multi-language)<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Make your website accessible to visitors worldwide with Travel Explorer\'s compatibility with popular multi-language translation plugins WPML and Polylang.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Regular Updates with Feature Enhancements&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>We continuously update our themes and plugins to ensure they are always compatible with the latest WordPress version. This way, you can be assured that your website is well-protected against vulnerabilities and includes all the latest features.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Extensive and Beginner-Friendly Documentation<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>Our team has created our documentation to make it as user-friendly as possible. Even if you have no prior expertise, our easy-to-understand documentation will walk you through the entire process of setting up your website step by step.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:heading {\\\"level\\\":3} -->\\n<h3 class=\\\"wp-block-heading\\\">Top-notch Quick and Friendly Support<\\/h3>\\n<!-- \\/wp:heading -->\\n\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\n<p>If you have any questions, comments, or feature requests regarding the theme, please contact our support team. We\'ll get back to you as soon as possible to help.<\\/p>\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\",\n                \"excerpt\": \"\",\n                \"thumbnail\": \"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/07\\/Travel-Explorer-theme.png\",\n                \"category\": [\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 7,\n                        \"name\": \"Free\",\n                        \"slug\": \"free\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 7,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 9,\n                        \"count\": 5,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    },\n                    {\n                        \"term_id\": 9,\n                        \"name\": \"Travel WordPress Themes\",\n                        \"slug\": \"travel-wordpress-themes\",\n                        \"term_group\": 0,\n                        \"term_taxonomy_id\": 9,\n                        \"taxonomy\": \"download_category\",\n                        \"description\": \"\",\n                        \"parent\": 0,\n                        \"count\": 9,\n                        \"filter\": \"raw\"\n                    }\n                ],\n                \"tags\": false,\n                \"image\": \"<img width=\\\"150\\\" height=\\\"150\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2023\\/