loads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Trips-Embedder-button.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22921\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Trips-Embedder-button.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1094\\\" height=\\\"325\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\n\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Popup.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22945\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/Popup.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"1323\\\" height=\\\"862\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The embedded trips are then shown right in-between your posts\\/page content to the visitors. Visitors can easily view the trips in the grid ( with carousel ) or list layout and access to get more details of the trip.<\\/span>\\n\\n<strong>Grid Layout<\\/strong>\\n\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/grid.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22925\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/grid.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"985\\\" height=\\\"559\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\n\\n<strong>List Layout<\\/strong>\\n\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/list.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22926\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/list.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"973\\\" height=\\\"496\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon also introduces <\\/span><b>new exciting Gutenberg Blocks<\\/b><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\"> for WP Travel Engine plugin. You can now insert your trips in a list or grid with ease even with the new WordPress Gutenberg Editor.<\\/span>\\n\\n[gallery size=\\\"full\\\" columns=\\\"2\\\" link=\\\"none\\\" ids=\\\"22930,22933\\\"]\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Blogs and information pages play a vital role in Travel and Tour company business as they are the gateway for potential travelers seeking information\\/suggestions through your website. Blog articles are also a good source of information that potential travelers seek out.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\n\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon lets you easily embed your trips in your blog articles and pages. Having the list of your recommended trips in a concise list or grid layout lets the readers have a glance at related trips right while reading the content and helps in better conversion towards the trips.<\\/span>\\n<h2><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Addon Features<\\/span><\\/h2>\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Simple and effective UI<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The addon is simple to install and use with no additional configurations required. After installing and activating the addon, new content editor button and Gutenberg Blocks are available to use and embed your trips to new and old blog posts and pages easily as per your requirements.\\u00a0<\\/span>\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Embedder layout options<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Embedder addon provides two different layouts to display your selected trips. A grid layout, with a carousel and list layout, can be chosen as per your requirements. Both layouts are concise and effective to show maximum information about trips chosen to display.<\\/span>\\n\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/layout.png\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-full wp-image-22940\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/wptravelengine.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/edd\\/2019\\/11\\/layout.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"918\\\" height=\\\"524\\\" \\/><\\/a>\\n<h3><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Number of posts options<\\/span><\\/h3>\\n<span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Trips Em